---
// About.astro — About section with mission/vision and trust indicators
---

<section id="nosotros" class="section about-section">
  <div class="about-glow glow-orb glow-orb-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label reveal">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        Nosotros
      </span>
      <h2 class="reveal" data-delay="0.1">Somos <span class="text-gradient">División Digital</span></h2>
      <p class="reveal" data-delay="0.2">
        Un equipo apasionado por transformar negocios a través de tecnología
        e-commerce de vanguardia y soluciones de inteligencia artificial.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- Mission -->
      <div class="about-card card reveal" data-delay="0.2">
        <div class="about-card-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Nuestra Misión</h3>
        <p>
          Democratizar el comercio electrónico brindando plataformas tecnológicas accesibles, potentes
          y con inteligencia artificial integrada. Cada negocio merece vender en línea de forma profesional.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Vision -->
      <div class="about-card card reveal" data-delay="0.3">
        <div class="about-card-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Nuestra Visión</h3>
        <p>
          Ser la agencia líder en soluciones e-commerce con IA en Latinoamérica,
          impulsando la transformación digital de miles de empresas con tecnología innovadora.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Values -->
      <div class="about-card card reveal" data-delay="0.4">
        <div class="about-card-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Nuestros Valores</h3>
        <p>
          Innovación constante, calidad premium en cada línea de código,
          transparencia total con nuestros clientes y compromiso con resultados medibles.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Trust indicators -->
    <div class="trust-bar reveal" data-delay="0.4">
      <div class="trust-item">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/></svg>
        <span>Código Seguro</span>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-divider"></div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="1" y="4" width="22" height="16" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="1" y1="10" x2="23" y2="10"/></svg>
        <span>Pagos Integrados</span>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-divider"></div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H6a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg>
        <span>Soporte Premium</span>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-divider"></div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
        <span>Alto Rendimiento</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-glow {
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    left: -200px;
    top: 30%;
    opacity: 0.06;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .about-card {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about-card-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent-subtle);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .about-card h3 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-card p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Trust bar */
  .trust-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-2xl);
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .trust-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .trust-item svg {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .trust-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 24px;
    background: var(--glass-border-subtle);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .trust-bar {
      gap: var(--space-lg);
      padding: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .trust-divider {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
